snippet.title: JO-Rush - Project Announcement Video
snippet.description:
Here we are everyone. 3 years in the making. Thank you to everyone who has followed the development of this project. There is still a lot of work left to do but for now, enjoy the video!

You can catch more updates on both Twitter and GameJolt!

Twitter:  https://twitter.com/SonicProjectJ1
GameJolt: https://gamejolt.com/games/sonicprojectj/426268
